2) Home & Kitchen - The product is used to secure cabinets, which is a common item found in kitchens and homes.
3) Office Products - Although less likely, the product could also be used in office settings to secure cabinets or drawers.
4) Tools & Home Improvement - The product can be considered a home improvement tool as it helps enhance safety and security in the home.
5) Pet Supplies - While less likely, the product could also be used to secure cabinets or drawers containing pet supplies to prevent pets from accessing them.

Please note that the categorization may vary depending on the specific platform or website where the product is listed.
